Lokomotiv Hockey Team Disaster



Aired on 03/04/2013, Narrated by Stephen Bogaert



On 7 September 2011, an aircraft, a Yakovlev Yak-42D, carrying the Lokomotiv Yaroslavl professional ice hockey team crashes shortly after take-off at Yaroslavl, Russia, resulting in the deaths of all but one of the 45 people aboard.
